</tbody>
</table>

<h3>Conclusion</h3>
<p>The following link finds all products that are in the genre of "Beginning Reader" and in the subject of "Science". The results are sorted by name in descending order:</p>

<pre><code>http://demo.titleleaf.com/products/search_results?order=name_desc&amp;search%5Bgenres_contains%5D=beginning_reader&amp;search%5Bcategories_id_in%5D%5B%5D=4
</code>
</pre>

<p>If you intend to use such a link in an email, it is highly recommended that you employ a URL shortening service such as <a href="https://bitly.com">Bitly</a>.</p>